Create a Autoscaling Group 
	
	Autoscaling Group - Create New - Name  - and select Launch Template - Version Type - VPC - Select subnets Min 2 - 
	
	Load Balancer Choose if any LB configured (depends basis if	need)- Group Size (Desired Capacity - Minimum Capacity - Maximum Capacity) - Scaling Policy - Enable instance scale-in protection - Verify configurations - Create 
	
	
		*	Once autoscaling group create option given, it will start to create new instances as mentioned in the Minimum capacity measures
		
       		
		
		
